<br>
“So you don’t think I’m nice and pretty?” Lex laughed and leaned into the car, so that his face was close to her ear.<br>
<br>
“I didn’t say that.” His raspy deep whisper made a shiver run through her body. He kissed her cheek and stood up straight. “Drive home safely.” He chuckled to himself and walked back to his car. Chloe sat in her dad’s car and placed a hand up to her cheek in astonishment.<br>
