<br>
“I’m sure Dad.” She walked over and zipped up his suitcase. He grinned and gave her a half concerned, half guilty look.<br>
<br>
“The convention’s only for a couple of days, and you can always call the Kents.” Chloe rolled her eyes, but smiled.<br>
<br>
