<br>
“Just because I own the place doesn’t mean that I need to frequent it.” Chloe rolled her eyes.<br>
<br>
“Okay, so what about the convention my dad went to? You’re not attending that?” He chuckled and leaned closer to her.<br>
<br>
“That would kind of negate my motive for sending your dad to it the first place, don’t you think?” Her eyes grew a little wider.<br>
<br>
“Oh.” He leaned back.<br>
<br>
“You didn’t like the flowers?” She smiled.<br>
<br>
