<br>
“So…” Lex began.<br>
<br>
“So,” Chloe smiled, prompting the same response from Lex.<br>
<br>
“Your father is out of town tonight, what are your plans for dinner?” Chloe laughed and partially rolled her eyes.<br>
<br>
“That was subtle,” she commented, the sarcasm evident. He smiled.<br>
<br>
“I wasn’t really going for subtle there, and I noticed that you avoided answering my question.”<br>
<br>
